{"tid":829223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文化] 應唔應該廢除人名改用數字?","createTime":"2018-09-20T09:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T04:21:04.000Z","uid":83097,"like":12,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"8aceb21df1ad78d3b324417136e8cafd2bdf5981","tid":829223,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:28:27.000Z","msg":"我覺得人名背後帶有極大程度既父權義識<br />\ngender從來都係一個好複雜既social construct<br />\n人名永遠都透露左一個人既姓別<br />\n例如jessica係女人，tom係男人<br />\n點解到左廿一世紀我地都接受到呢種不知所謂既姓別定型?<br />\n用number黎稱呼人就含邏輯得多<br />\n例如12345，23456<br />\n大家點睇?<br />\n歡迎唔同意見，不過任何唔支持我既極右分仔麻煩出返去，我雖然tolerance但唔會接受ignorance<br />\n利申 : <br />\nmajor in gender studies + social science<br />\n細過係中學無朋友被人欺凌，大過發夢自己係英雄<br />\n屋企有錢所以從來都無返過工，可以專心研究點領導同指引其他低下階層低下種族<br />\n鐘意食大麻<br />\n支持多元文化，雖然無白人之外既唔同膚色朋友"},{"pid":"e84059c727c97672e3522e6b2ef1b503059cedfe","tid":829223,"uid":159086,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"監犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e6f9f7711d4728504dbccb21d72cf3659b3f29","tid":829223,"uid":19524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"6ix9ine <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0a39a17ccc65cd98759a4e9d26bbd4ea459a24","tid":829223,"uid":96843,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:36:44.000Z","msg":"好似毛魔係中國實行過呢樣野，連毛魔都做唔到就可想而知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ba2031996fb46aaddce1ae7a3ef5b34d83ddfe","tid":829223,"uid":187227,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09